#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/time_materials.rst:278
msgid ""
"First, add a :guilabel:`Vendor` to the purchase order. Then, under the "
":guilabel:`Products` tab, click the :guilabel:`extra column options` drop-"
